  • Package src.entities

    • Class src.entities.Cinema

      class Cinema extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • cinemaName
          String cinemaName
          This Cinema's name
        • movies
          ArrayList<Movie> movies
          Array list of movies to store all movies in this Cinema
        • prices
          HashMap<String,Double> prices
          A HashMap for Staff to set prices in this Cinema String for associated movie title and Double for the price
        • seats
          HashMap<String,ArrayList<Seat>> seats
          HashMap of seats in this Cinema String indicates movie and showtime while array list of Seat is to store the details of each Seat
        • showtimes
          HashMap<String,ArrayList<LocalDateTime>> showtimes
          HashMap of showtimes for movies in this Cinema String indicates movie title and Array list of LocalDateTime for fixed showtimes
